title: A Fashion Show WITH Fashions
description: Join Casey and Danielle, along with the rest of the world, in mourning (although nothing to do with The Monarchy and everything to do with SHE By Shein). They are joined by the hilarious and gorgeous Jana Schmieding (Rutherford Falls) who is just as startled as Casey is by Danielles oddly arrogant and personal take away from Sheree’s fashion show. Enjoy!
